Package edu.umn.cs.spatialHadoop.delaunay

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DelaunayTriangulation
    Computes the Delaunay triangulation (DT) for a set of points.
    DelaunayTriangulation.DelaunayMap<S extends Point>
    The map function computes the DT for a partition and splits the triangulation into safe and non-safe edges.
    DelaunayTriangulation.DelaunayReduce
    Reduce function for DT.
    DelaunayTriangulationOutputFormat
    Writes the results of the DelaunayTriangulation operation and merges non-final results upon the completion of all reducers.
    DelaunayTriangulationOutputFormat.TriangulationMerger  
    DelaunayTriangulationOutputFormat.TriangulationRecordWriter  
    GSDTAlgorithm
    The divide and conquer Delaunay Triangulation (DT) algorithm as proposed in L.
    SimpleGraph
    A class to store the output of Dealaunay Triangulation as a graph.
